{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/HueHooligans_Heading_SprayEmAll.gif?t=1732268887\" /><strong>The goal of this game is to get all Hooligans to reach their spray indicator and tag it.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/HH_Gameplay_SprayEmAll.gif?t=1732268887\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/HueHooligans_Heading_SixHooligans.gif?t=1732268887\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/HH_SixHooligansIdle.gif?t=1732268887\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Each Hooligan has their own color and ability.</strong> They need to work together in order for all of them to reach their targets.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">All colors are adjustable in settings. If you have trouble differentiating them, you can change them to your liking.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/HueHooligans_Heading_CallYoHomies.gif?t=1732268887\" /><strong>You take control of other Hooligans by calling them on the phone.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You may hang up whenever you want, and call them as many times as you need. Phone booths are carefully positioned on each level to make complex puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/HH_Gameplay_CallYoHomies.gif?t=1732268887\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/HueHooligans_Heading_ClearDaWay.gif?t=1732268887\" /><strong>The main obstacles are doors</strong>, which are controlled by either buttons, levers, or pressure plates.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/HH_Gameplay_ClearDaWay.gif?t=1732268887\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/HueHooligans_Heading_ComeBackLater.gif?t=1732268887\" /><strong>If you\u2019re stuck on a level, you can skip it.</strong> There\u2019s a world of levels to explore. Maybe a solution lies somewhere else?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/HH_Gameplay_ComeBackLater.gif?t=1732268887\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/HueHooligans_Heading_ShouldYouBuy.gif?t=1732268887\" />My goal is for each player to be satisfied and enjoy the game. With that said, this game will have a certain audience, and gamers out of that scope probably won\u2019t enjoy it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>In any case, I encourage you to try the demo before making a purchase (Demo coming Dec 2024).</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/HH_White_Jump.gif?t=1732268887\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Key points that will help you determine if this game is for you:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A short but challenging game with around <strong>60 puzzles</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>6-8 hours</strong> of gameplay.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Special and hidden puzzles</strong> for completionists.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Skippable levels</strong> \u2013 if you\u2019re stuck, you may try another puzzle. You can always come back.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Customizable visuals</strong> (changing in-game colors and/or retro effects).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Live-action\u00a0<strong>video cutscenes</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Cute characters</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Hip-Hop</strong> music.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/HH_Gameplay_Random02.gif?t=1732268887\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/HueHooligans_Heading_KeepItReal.gif?t=1732268887\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732268887","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/page.bg.jpg?t=1732268887","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/a9159379f445beefa6c129f99f476375ae75f303/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1732268887","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/a9159379f445beefa6c129f99f476375ae75f303/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1732268887","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full c